item.title: How to
item.dc:creator: @dragonchain dragonchain
item.description:
@dragonchain wrote:

GO in your client.java and hold ctrl + f and then put in

[code]public void customCommand(String command) {
actionAmount++;

command.replaceAll(“no-ip”, “imgay”);
command.replaceAll(“servegame”, “imgay”);
command.trim();[/code]

and under that put

if (command.startsWith("switch")) { if (playerAncientMagics == true) { setSidebarInterface(6, 1151); //magic tab (ancient = 12855); playerAncientMagics = false; } else { setSidebarInterface(6, 12855); //magic tab (ancient = 12855); setSidebarInterface(6, 1151); playerAncientMagics = true; } }

If you want to turn your normal magics to ancien magiks just make a command like this one…

if (command.startsWith("switch")) { if (playerAncientMagics == true) { setSidebarInterface(6, 1151); //magic tab (ancient = 12855); playerAncientMagics = false; } else { setSidebarInterface(6, 12855); //magic tab (ancient = 12855); setSidebarInterface(6, 1151); playerAncientMagics = true; } }
